{"tid":1972412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民調: 美國公眾對中國態度跌至歷史新低，而且唔只因為疫情","createTime":"2020-04-14T13:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T14:31:56.000Z","uid":305299,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a19fa40141aaa2fda2802c6e506adf35e37ccd29","tid":1972412,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"我地係咪要把握時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多上 twitter 踩多幾腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其居然美國人仲覺得可以同中國進行建設性交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下而係我好粗糙咁翻譯咗篇報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/us-public-opinion-toward-china-is-at-an-all-time-low-and-its-not-solely-about-the-coronavirus-2020-04-13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketwatch.com%2Fstory%2Fus-public-opinion-toward-china-is-at-an-all-time-low-and-its-not-solely-about-the-coronavirus-2020-04-13&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=29e57c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.marketwatch.com/story/us-public-opinion-toward-china-is-at-an-all-time-low-and-its-not-solely-about-the-coronavirus-2020-04-13</a><br />\n<br />\n美國上星期嘅民調顯示，美國公眾對中國嘅負面態度升至1970年代開始有紀錄以來最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據紀錄，美國歷史上只有三次，美國公眾對中國嘅正面態度係大於負面態度，分別為1979年中國對外開放，1989年天安門大屠殺之前嘅民主運動，同埋第三次，最近一次，亦係最奇怪一次，2018年係貿易戰之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自此，就一直向下，原因包括貿易戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港民主抗議</span>，維吾爾族集中營，南海領土主張進一步加強，以及特朗普所講嘅中國經濟犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而上星期嘅民調更顯示，美國人普遍認為，中國對全球當前嘅大流行要負責任，而且喺在貿易、武漢肺炎等重要問題嘅資信以及其他地緣政治問題上都唔值得信賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n調查同時顯示，美國絕大多數人支持對中國實施「更強硬貿易政策」。受訪者仲表示，如果中國唔履行第一階段貿易承諾，就應該採取懲罰性措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，儘管如此，民調發現，美國人仍然希望同中國進行建設性交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4b3cbab415529a7b58d3acbf9a8010e1c85fc1","tid":1972412,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"8d9137602b306799991a4e5acb8a7ba6955f1a21","tid":1972412,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"美國佬今舖肺炎仲未知驚"},{"pid":"c4006ffe66aa2753f539a33d5bc98b487ba40b4e","tid":1972412,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"吸收左泰國盟友既文宣技巧<br />\n撥火師係時候進入新境界了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4b0b6b34b96684020ff4d2b330db5fd2f27b64","tid":1972412,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"支共在經濟、安全、生命、精神都對美國人民造成傷害，美國官員庫德洛證實<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u_D_cXuDJWI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu_D_cXuDJWI&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=846bd733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u_D_cXuDJWI</a>"},{"pid":"7d9a9ae5ffb1036862afd9fc6bd31087c69d58ed","tid":1972412,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98235e31b6f3aa784acd7db482ebac4f1ecc74a2","tid":1972412,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:31:56.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主，國際戰線要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}